<Base title="Fresh Pantry — Support" doc>
  <nav><a href="/freshpantry/">← Fresh Pantry</a></nav>
  <h1>Support</h1>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>Email us at <a href="mailto:support@sunpebblelabs.com">support@sunpebblelabs.com</a> —
     we usually reply within two days.</p>

  <h2>Sync not catching up?</h2>
  <p>Fresh Pantry is local-first: changes save on your device immediately and sync when you're
     online. A pending-sync badge means the app is waiting for a connection — your data is safe.</p>

  <h2>Sign-in code not arriving?</h2>
  <p>Check your spam folder for the 6-digit code. Codes expire after a few minutes; request a
     new one from the sign-in screen if needed.</p>
</Base>
